{"type":null,"faqId":45413,"title":"华为盒子如何连接功放，组建家庭影院？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>华为盒子有三种连接功放的方式：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方式一（推荐）： </span><span>准备SPDIF 线（官方配件）、功放</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>按照下图完成连线。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>进入“</span><span class=\"s1\">设置 &gt; 播放 &gt; AV 音视频</span><span>”，选择 “</span><span class=\"s1\">SPDIF 音频源码输出</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165031\" style=\"width:3.2555556in;height:2.917361in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方式二：</span><span>准备HDMI 线、功放</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>按照下图完成连线。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>进入“</span><span class=\"s1\">设置 &gt; 播放 &gt; HDMI 音频</span><span>”，选择 “</span><span class=\"s1\">HDMI 音频源码输出</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165032\" style=\"width:3.2166667in;height:2.95625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方式三：</span><span>准备AV 符合视频线（官方配件）、功放</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>按照下图完成连线。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>进入“</span><span class=\"s1\">设置 &gt; 播放 &gt; AV 音视频</span><span>”，选择 “</span><span class=\"s1\">CVBS 音频源码输出</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165033\" style=\"width:3.2166667in;height:2.99375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":242,"faqType":"安装产品","useful":5,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"933","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Setting-Up","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442557780000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":31,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"连接,功放,家庭影院","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}